const  pluckDeep  =  key  =>  obj  =>  key.split('.').reduce((accum, key) =>  accum[key], obj)

const  compose  = (...fns) =>  res  =>  fns.reduce((accum, next) =>  next(accum), res)

const  unfold  = (f, seed) => {
 const  go  = (f, seed, acc) => {
   const  res  =  f(seed)
   return  res  ?  go(f, res[1], acc.concat([res[0]])) : acc
}
 return  go(f, seed, [])
}
